message.body: Have any other interviews this week?
That's still pretty loud then.
None so far.
I'm trying to recall how we got to talking about faith earlier.
About being religious?
Yes. I don't know but I try to reflect on those convos now and then. It's kind of my weakest point to defend/discuss
It could be a very personal topic for some people.
It is. I rarely feel comfortable talking it about. Especially with family.
You mentioned I am responsible for my siblings being not Catholic because I'm not. I never told them not to believe. But I think they realized they didn't believe either and asked me about it. @
It's your own personal beliefs. You don't have to share it if you don't want to.
It's a possibility.
I simply said just go to church with the parents until you're 18 or whenever you can better defend the point to them.
Okay.
That's what I did at least lol. It's possible that my mother feels better by us simply being in his house, faith or not
Uh huh.
What is it?
What is what?
I wasn't sure if what I'm saying is odd I to you or I'm catching you at a bad time. Or I'm reading too much into the tiny responses.
No, nothing bad. Didn't know if you were finished.
I'm sending short responses as an indication that I following you.
*i'm
Gotcha. Like nodding lol
Yup.
I guess in the end, I sometimes wish I had a better answer to give my parents when they ask why I don't go to church.
I can think of several reasons why people don't go, but again, the reason(s) why you choose not to go is your own.
Religion is complicated
That's true. I think I found a potential eatery list for the summer http://www.thrillist.com/eat/philadelphia/best-new-restaurants-in-philadelphia-spring-2015
It takes time to figure it out.
Indeed. It's like I'm speaking a foreign language when I say I just don't believe. It becomes incomprehensible to them that someone doesn't believe
Already planning your meals for the summer?
Guess you really like to plan ahead.
Guilty as charged. I like taking the guess work out if I can.
Because when you get hungry and want to try out a new place, making that decision isn't easy on an empty stomach
I can see that happening.
Watch "The most awesome Omurice in Kichi2, Kyoto Japan" https://youtu.be/Uu5zGHjRaMo Are you ready for a most satisfying omelette video?
Hahah I'm not a bug fan of omelet totes.
*omelettes
This may pique your interest =P
Do you eat a lot of omelettes?
Kinda. I mostly do scrambled egg sandwiches for breakfast.
If I'm out and about I'll grab omelettes at a breakfast joint
That sounds good. Eggs are so versatile and delicious.
Yeah. I love eggs. They can top almost anything. Sit on Vietnamese rice dish. Ramen. Etc
Truth
It would suck being allergic
Don't scare me!
I'm so terrified about the idea of becoming allergic to anything I enjoy consuming
I agree.
I knew someone who was allergic to water.
That really sux.
No way. How did they live? You know, being made of 70 % water and all
I think I remember her saying that she takes a pill every day.
That's not too bad so long as she doesn't forget
But that's pretty inconvenient though.
Think of it like contacts. Although it isn't life threatening it just becomes second nature.
My moment of "really guys?" yesterday: the three of them (Cindy Scott and Thuy) agreed to go rock climbing and once we get there all three say they're actually afraid of heights.
Hahah did they end u
*up climbing?
No, we left for food then went bowling
What? Oh man.
I know lol. Good times.
Can you talk?
In a few minutes. Wrapping up an email. I'll call ya after?
Are you sure?
Yeah it's fine. I'd tell say so if otherwise.
Can we talk at 1?
Sure.
Thanks!
Sorry am I calling you?
Stanley isn't too happy about Monday either. http://imgur.com/21BKhXb
Hey. Hope you're a bit better!
Hey, I'm okay. I want to ask if you are. You sounded down earlier, is something wrong?
You mean on the phone just today? No I'm ok for now lol. I was just finishing some dead lifts when you had called
Oh okay. Just making sure.
Thank you, you're such a sweet gal.
Getting sleepy. I need to stay up until bed time lol.
Guess who just got up from a nap?
ï¿¼
Haha. Looks like he's ready for mischief!
Always.
Just scratched my face!
Oh no! Did he break skin?
I hope not.
So that means you have a week left to mostly enjoy yourself. If I understood you correctly.
I guess. Turns out, we're not going to Texas so I can start sooner. But I think I'm going to give myself a few days, two make it like two weeks which is the standard right?
That is correct
So where is the office gonna be at?
18th and Market.
I just home from my sister's.
Man, I babysat for a week!
Can't believe I did all that for a week.
You're a trooper it seems
I think the real heroes are the parents. It's non stop for them.
How's your night going?
It is. But it's a different perspective when you're the parent. Oh man you'll be next to nom nom ramen. Great place
I've never heard of that.
I ate the steak from Saturday for dinner lol. Settled in with house of cards on Netflix
Sounds like a great night.
I might do that. But with rice, no cheese, and bit House of Cards hahah.
Heh. Where are you in the series?
Never started.
So prior to the beginning?
Haha.
Oh man. Saddle in. You're in for a wild ride. I wish I could watch the first season for the first time again
That good huh?
Do you have any good restaurant recommendations?
I may have some bias because of Kevin. Depends. Where? Kind of food? Atmosphere?
I'm just looking to brainstorm ideas right now.
So anything in Philadelphia.
Ahh. For your 21st?
Hahah that's sweet. If only. I'm old.
Let me look through my old check ins to jog my memory and I'll let you know
Thanks!
See if you got an email from me
Yup!
Ok I'm writing up a short blurb in each because I didn't know how to copy the list originally
No, that's too much work!
I can look up descriptions if the places myself.
Thanks for the list!!!
I kinda like vouching (Not in my dictionary oddly enough?) for my suggestions
Hmm. I wonder if I can work on a bar and cheap eats list next lol
That would be a good one!
What do you think if what I sent so far?
Of*
I've heard of some of these places. Hahah I like the descriptions, pretty sassy there.
I'll tell out how I see it ^_^
It*
How's house of cards?
Uyen says call Brittany
Didn't start. I don't have Netflix.
Hahah thanks for passing the message along.
How many seasons are there?
There are 3. I can give you them on a flash drive if you were so inclined to see them.
No way, would that be a lot of work?
I download all the shows I watch. Not a big deal.
Are you sure?
Yeah. I'll let you know when it's ready. Do you care if it's in HD? I don't download those because they take up a huge amount of space
